OL,7,Fcondition in hospital following a hit
OL,8,Fand run.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,FPromenade in Southport just before 9pm
OL,12,Fon Monday 4 December following reports
OL,13,Fof a crash involving a blue Volkswagen
OL,14,FBora Sport car.
OL,16,FThe electric wheelchair user, a man in
OL,17,Fhis 40s, was treated at the scene for
OL,18,Fserious leg injuries and taken to
OL,19,Fhospital where he remains in a
OL,20,Fcritical condition.
